## üõ†Ô∏è Development

```bash
# clone & setup venv
git clone https://github.com/agent-matrix/matrix-cli.git
cd matrix-cli
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate

# install dev deps
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# lint & format
ruff check .
black .

# run tests
pytest
```

